Lydia Rose Bewley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lydia_Rose_Bewley 0 Lydia Rose Bewley (born 9 October 1985) is an English actress known for her role as Jane in The Inbetweeners Movie and Matella in Plebs. She trained at Oxford School of Drama before working in repertory theatre.
